{"prompt": "Design a professional portfolio for a freelance journalist. The aesthetic should incorporate a classic charcoal grey.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Jane Doe - Freelance Journalist</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #0779e4 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        #about, #portfolio, #contact {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #fff;\n            border-left: 5px solid #333;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #333;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            background: #f9f9f9;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item a {\n            color: #333;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item a:hover {\n            color: #0779e4;\n        }\n        #contact form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #contact form input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact form input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        #contact form button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact form button:hover {\n            background: #555;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Jane Doe</h1>\n            <p>Investigative & Feature Journalist</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"main-content\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>A seasoned freelance journalist with a passion for uncovering compelling stories and delivering in-depth reporting. Specializing in [mention your specializations, e.g., social justice, technology, travel], I bring a critical eye and a commitment to factual accuracy to every piece.</p>\n            <p>My work has been featured in numerous publications, and I am dedicated to crafting narratives that inform, engage, and inspire readers.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Featured Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>The Future of Urban Farming</h3>\n                <p>An in-depth exploration of innovative farming techniques transforming city landscapes. Published in [Publication Name].</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>Behind the Gig Economy</h3>\n                <p>A series of profiles revealing the realities faced by freelance workers in the modern economy. Featured in [Publication Name].</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>The Art of Sustainable Travel</h3>\n                <p>A guide to responsible tourism and its impact on local communities and the environment. Available in [Publication Name].</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Read More</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Jane Doe. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}